Enum QueueMsgType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<QueueMsgType>
      • com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.queue.QueueMsgType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<QueueMsgType>

    public enum QueueMsgType
extends java.lang.Enum<QueueMsgType>
    The types of RDM queue messages. rdmMsgType member in QueueMsg may be set to one of these to indicate the specific RDMQueueMsg class.
    See Also:
    QueueClose, QueueRefresh, QueueRequest, QueueStatus, QueueAck, QueueData, QueueDataExpired
